---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Reviews" description="See what customers are saying about TrueFix Auto in Colorado Springs. Real Google reviews from real customers.">

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <div class="section-label light">Customer Reviews</div>
      <h1 class="section-title light">DON'T TAKE<br>OUR WORD FOR IT.</h1>
      <p>Real reviews from real customers in Colorado Springs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rating-badge">
      <div class="rating-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <div class="rating-num">5.0</div>
      <div class="rating-source">on Google Reviews</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- REVIEWS GRID -->
  <section class="reviews-section">

    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I was new in the area and they took their time to explain everything and went above and beyond for my vehicle. Very honest and fair prices. If I have an issue I stop by and they always make time to help — always in a very fair and honest manner."</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Anahi Rodriguez</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"As a woman it is difficult finding an honest mechanic. I really appreciate their fairness in price — they didn't leave until my vehicle was fixed. Talked to me in terms I could understand, made a very stressful day easy to deal with. I wish I would've found them sooner! Phenomenal service."</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Anne Lee Romero</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I brought in my 2003 Buick LeSabre for squeaky brakes and a check engine light. Cowboy kept me updated the entire time, found a coolant leak I didn't know about, very reasonable prices, didn't try to upcharge, and my car was done the same day. Highly highly recommend!!"</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Eden Mae Yates</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Cowboy Mechanic Shop is fantastic! I was greeted with a smile, given an honest estimate within my budget, and there was no upcharging. My car was ready quickly and not stuck in the shop for days. Honest, fast, affordable and veteran-owned. Highly recommend!"</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Anthony Rivera</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Super professional and great communication. They did everything they said they would. Their honest opinion on certain parts I thought may need fixed — they said they'd be fine and pointed out actual priority things instead. I'll definitely recommend them to anybody."</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Camden Burton</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Great service! Got an oil change and an alignment — good price and good people. Would absolutely recommend to anyone in Colorado Springs looking for an honest mechanic."</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Robens Auzirus</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="reviews-see-all">
      <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Cowboys+Mechanic+Shop+Colorado+Springs+Reviews&ludocid=18315268684440215550" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">See All Google Reviews →</a>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 72px 80px 60px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .page-header-inner p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.5);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .rating-badge {
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(30,125,52,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,125,52,0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 36px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .rating-stars {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--green-light);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rating-num {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .rating-source {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.4);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* REVIEWS */
  .reviews-section {
    padding: 72px 80px;
    background: var(--green-pale);
  }

  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .review-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .review-card.featured { border-left-width: 4px; }
  .review-card.placeholder-card { border-left-color: var(--border); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

  .stars {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .review-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-style: italic;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .placeholder-text {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .review-footer {}
  .review-author {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .review-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-top: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .leave-review-link {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .leave-review-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .reviews-see-all {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header { padding: 48px 24px 40px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 28px; }
    .rating-badge { width: 100%; padding: 20px; }
    .reviews-section { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .google-cta { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .google-cta-inner h2 { font-size: 32px; }
  }
</style>